  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江社团一档写作类社刊，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/mag/135231930/\" style=\"color: rgb(0,90,148); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江社团订阅本社刊！</p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201512/70b239c8-f1ee-4fb1-9dbb-7c152b26e20e.jpg\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(16,113,181); font-size: 14px; text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"点击查看原图\"><img src=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201512/70b239c8-f1ee-4fb1-9dbb-7c152b26e20e.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px; height: 332px;\" /></a><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 16px; font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\t<a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Buffet\" target=\"_blank\">Buffet</a><br />\n\tA buffet is a side cabinet placed on the ground. What does the buffet look like? Where is it found? What items can be found inside the buffet?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They searched the buffet... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) purchasing a buffet for the room<br />\n\t2) dropped an item behind the buffet<br />\n\t3) trying to move the buffet during re-decoration<br />\n\t4) hiding an object inside the buffet<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t&quot;There you are,&quot; he said to himself when he picked up his pen. When he was about to get up, something caught his eye. In a discrete corner, on the underside edge of a waist-high buffet, he saw a bug. Of course it was not an insect type of bug; it was an audio surveillance type of bug. The coin-sized black bug was stealthy tugged into the shadows. Had the interior designer not scoped that low, the equipment would be difficult to detect. For a short moment, he stared at the bug.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/166887191194/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p767195/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p767195\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p767427/\">陪跑22年的血泪史！这次咱小李子终于圆满了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p767861/\">小李子获奥斯卡影帝感言全文：附语言点精析</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p766962/\">BBC纪录片《中国新年》全集 附超全笔记精华</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p767607/\">跟我是歌手学英文：李玟What's Up</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p767768/\">英语水平止步不前，学习方法找对了吗？</a></li><li style=\"