  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://img.wdjimg.com/mms/icon/v1/b/7a/1b7ac6f8826971800db4c448dc1637ab_256_256.png\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p765876\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\tAnd we start with writer and producer Anthony McCarten whose film, The Theory of Everything, has four <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/nomination\" target=\"_blank\">nominations</a> including Best Actor nod for Eddie Redmayne <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/scorchingly\" target=\"_blank\">scorchingly</a> tipped to win for his performance as Professor Stephen Hawking. McCarten has two nominations for Best Film and Best Adapted Screenplay of Jane Hawking's memoir about her marriage to the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/theoretical\" target=\"_blank\">theoretical</a> <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/physicist\" target=\"_blank\">physicist</a>. It's a film many have found moving for being more interested in the minutiae and nuances of family life as it is in any scientific Eureka moments. I spoke to Anthony slightly worse for wear the morning after he'd won the BAFTA for his screenplay. And he told me that the accolades and nominations were a reward for ten years' hard work.</p>\n<p>\n\t&quot;In 2004, I read Jane Hawking's remarkable autobiography that really showed the journey she'd been on which was <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/initially\" target=\"_blank\">initially</a> meant to have been a two-year sort of deal that Stephen had been given a diagnosis of only two years to live. And on that basis, she had said, 'Yes, well, I'll make those two years as rich as we can and I love you.' Of course, as we know, the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/prognosis\" target=\"_blank\">prognosis</a> was wrong, thankfully, and this turned into a 27-year marriage and Jane very, very movingly, I think, describes that journey, the highs, the lows, and I thought that is such an extraordinary one-of-a-kind love story.&quot;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>声明：音视频均来自互联网链接，仅供学习使用。本网站自身不存储、控制、修改被链接的内容。&ldquo;沪江</span><a>英语</a><span>&rdquo;高度重视知识产权保护。当如发现本网站发布的信息包含有侵犯其著作权的链接内容时，请联系我们，我们将依法采取措施移除相关内容或屏蔽相关链接。&gt;&gt;<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/course/52569?source=16553\" style=\"color: rgb(0,90,148); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">零基础直达流利生活口语班</a>&lt;&lt;</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p765876/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p765876\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p767427/\">陪跑22年的血泪史！这次咱小李子终于圆满了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p767861/\">小李子获奥斯卡影帝感言全文：附语言点精析</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p766962/\">BBC纪录片《中国新年》全集 附超全笔记精华</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p767607/\">跟我是歌手学英文：李玟What's Up</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p767768/\">英语水平止步不前，学习方法找对了吗？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p767791/\">BBC这纪录片逆天！英皇室八卦秘闻没放过1个</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p767699/\">奥斯卡红毯：杰克露丝再次合体Gaga仙气十足</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p767317/\">四级没过，别哭，看这里！！！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p767829/\">囧研究：11为啥英文不叫ONETEEN？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p7676